_sText:
Thank you for looking at my map! This is a good level for awp, close range, and many other things. This map can hold up to thirty 32 people without getting stuck or having the map be too small for the amount of players. There are two main sniping/assault bunkers on each side of the map, six bunkers down below, barrels and a truck. I will make a new release soon!

RLhockey203
